name: Version 6.0.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Improve local development scripts and build system by @tilfin in https://github.com/tilfinltd/aws-extend-switch-roles/pull/359
* Upgrade devDependencies libraries by @tilfin in https://github.com/tilfinltd/aws-extend-switch-roles/pull/360
* Fix calling hasOwn in setup_manifest.mjs by @tilfin in https://github.com/tilfinltd/aws-extend-switch-roles/pull/361
* Support prism mode by @tilfin in https://github.com/tilfinltd/aws-extend-switch-roles/pull/362


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/tilfinltd/aws-extend-switch-roles/compare/v5.0.2...v6.0.0

name: v0.13.1
body: - Fix that the switch role definition in the same AWS Account ID causes the list to be empty

name: v0.13.0
body:
- Support 'target_role_name' parameter that expresses the role name for target roles, on base account
- Fix excluding unrelated profiles from role history

name: v0.12.1
body:
* Enlarge profile image icon
* Fix configuration textarea not synchronized

name: v0.12.0
body:
- Textbox filtering supports by account id (thanks to @heldersepu)
- Fix auto switch last role feature
- Support AWS GovCloud (experimental)

name: v0.11.0
body:
- Add image option (thanks to @timcleaver)
- Fix that a part of deleted profiles remaining (#66 #70)

name: v0.10.0
body: * Add new textbox that filters items by profile name and its 'Enter' key makes switching to first matched role

name: v0.9.0
body:
- Support the number of profiles maximum 200
- Add 'Credits' and 'Donation' links on popup menu

name: v0.8.1
body: * Fix finding profile on form submit (thanks to @craig-miskell-fluxfederation)

name: v0.8.0
body:
- Change the configuration from popup panel to another tab page
- Support new 'Automatically assume last assumed role' option (Experimental)
- Fix attaching color line broken

name: v0.7.0
body:
* Support A 'region' parameter can be used to change the region whenever switching the role.
* Fix *Show only matching roles* option has negative effect on normal AWS login

name: v0.6.3
body: * Added role filtering for use with federated AWS login by @robsweet
